snippet.title: The Rum Diary Amber Heard Makeup Tutorial
snippet.description:
Get this bronzy smokey eye with just a hint of carbon smoke for the Holiday season. Nikol shows you how to create this look using Fresh Beauty Studio cosmetics. Enter promo code YouTube30 at check out on www.freshbeautystudio.com for 30% off and FREE shipping on orders $75 or more. 
It's all about Hollywood sheen to the eye with this look. Embrace lip gloss is used with a touch of Nibble on top for a super plump lip. 
Follow for Beauty: www.twitter.com/freshmakeup
Blog: www.freshbeautystudio.com/blog
